  "insights": [
    "Revenue grew 18% YoY driven by expansion into enterprise accounts, with enterprise ARPA improving via bundled contracts.",
    "Churn rose from 3.1% to 4.0% after the pricing change, with mid-market and smaller customers showing higher downgrades/cancellations and slightly negative sentiment in mid-tier surveys.",
    "Support tickets increased 25%, mostly tied to billing confusion and feature access restrictions, indicating pricing/packaging clarity issues; marketing spend also rose 15%."
