  "risk": "Pricing/packaging changes are eroding retention and satisfaction in mid-market/smaller segments, potentially offsetting enterprise-led growth and increasing support costs.",
  "next_action": "Audit the pricing change impact by segment and address billing/feature-access confusion (clearer messaging, in-app entitlements, support macros), then test revised mid-market pricing/packaging to reduce churn and ticket volume."
